James Stewart (Australian actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Stewart_(Australian_actor) 0 James Stewart (born 21 October 1975) is an Australian stage, television and film actor, best known for his appearances in the television series Breakers and Packed to the Rafters. He has also made an appearance in the popular Australian drama Sea Patrol. From 2016, he began starring in Home and Away as Justin Morgan.
